    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is absolutely flawless\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it garaged and spotless. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
