      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior finish is deep and reflective, protected by a professional ceramic coating with absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin retains its original new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery is taut and unmarked, and every electronic component functions with precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who demands perfection. It comes complete with all original keys, documentation, and a spotless history report.",
