      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been kept spotless inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that feels basically brand new without the showroom price tag, this is the one. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love it!",
