      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 era. It features the factory-spec individual throttle bodies and a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission, delivering a visceral 8,400 RPM redline experience. The chassis is impeccably preserved, featuring Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and an M-variable differential lock that remains tight and responsive. This specimen has undergone meticulous preventative maintenance, including a documented rod bearing service and subframe inspection. Finished in pristine paint with zero clear coat failure, it sits on staggered forged Style 220M wheels. The interior exhibits no bolster wear or pixel degradation, representing a true turn-key investment for the enthusiast seeking a mechanically transparent and aesthetically flawless naturally aspirated icon.",
